===Noun===
'''relocation'''
#The act of [[moving]] from one [[place]] to [[another]]. Often refers to a service provided by a licensed [http://www.affordablemovingcompany.com/estimates/ mover] that packs and transport goods from location to destination. Relocation Services can include a variety or moving services including corporate employee relocation services which involves being moved by your company. Business relocation services is when a business is physically relocated and entails moving of infrastructure and equipment as well as employees. Household goods are gnerrally moved by [http://www.relocationmax.com/ moving companies] that provide moving services licensed by the Federal Motor Carriers Safety Administration.

